reviews.text: Good food and warm service. Reasonably priced. Excellent location, accessible by mtr buses and self driving.

I came here for the first time on December 8, 2018 for a round table set dinner. It is very accessible via the Lai Chee Kwok MTR station. As an eating place, the quality, service and price are all right!

Service is good but that's the only thing that is good at this place. We have eaten here a few times with relatives and every dish is just bad in terms of quality. We once even saw food dye in our green vegetables that wasn't mixed in. Avoid!
Delicious food
Too oily, small portions. Doesn't do chiu chow style justice.
